summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2014 JEEP CHEROKEE. WHILE DRIVING 5 MPH AND APPLYING THE ACCELERATOR PEDAL, THE VEHICLE FAILED TO RESPOND AND STALLED WITHOUT WARNING. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO A LOCAL DEALER (ADVANTAGE CHRYSLER DODGE JEEP LOCATED AT 18311 US HIGHWAY 441 MOUNT FORA, FL 32757 (352)-735-3777), BUT THE FAILURE COULD NOT BE DUPLICATED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 34,000.
